    org.springframework.web.socket.server.support

    • org.springframework.web.servlet.config.annotation中SimpleUrlHandlerMapping的使用

      返回SimpleUrlHandlerMapping的org.springframework.web.servlet.config.annotation中的方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      protected SimpleUrlHandlerMapping DefaultServletHandlerConfigurer.buildHandlerMapping()
      Return a handler mapping instance ordered at Ordered.LOWEST_PRECEDENCE containing the DefaultServletHttpRequestHandler instance mapped to "/**"; or null if default servlet handling was not been enabled.
      protected SimpleUrlHandlerMapping ViewControllerRegistry.buildHandlerMapping()
      Return the HandlerMapping that contains the registered view controller mappings, or null for no registrations.

    • org.springframework.web.socket.server.support中SimpleUrlHandlerMapping的使用

      org.springframework.web.socket.server.support中SimpleUrlHandlerMapping的子类 
      限定符和类型 类和说明
      class  WebSocketHandlerMapping
      An extension of SimpleUrlHandlerMapping that is also a SmartLifecycle container and propagates start and stop calls to any handlers that implement Lifecycle.
